US ($38 CAN for Canadian residents only) to:

                          M. Nelson
                          P.O. Box 53
                        Sarnia, Ontario
                        CANADA  N7T 7H8

    Print out the registration form (or otherwise provide me with the
information) and include it with your registration.

    Registered users will receive, by mail, a keyfile which will unlock
this all future versions of RIPGRAF. The keyfile allows you to load
RIPscrip files, use UNDO, and will save the buttons you create. It also
comes with a separate program, used to convert IFF image files into the
RIP icon (ICN) format.

